{
  "stem": "12289.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started to wonder, where are they?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was just a-- a couple of days after the arrival of the-- the-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were rumors already going around the city that the Germans, which proved to be right then, that they took key persons, like as hostages to go a little, whatever.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were all-- all deported to-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not that many, but a couple of hundred people, wealthy business people and all that, the key persons in the Jewish community, all of a sudden, just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wondered, what has happened now to this-- this Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Weiss, who stayed with us in the same house?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I started to-- to-- to-- to inquire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I heard that there was a camp just-- not far away from the embassy, kind of a first stage or provisional sort of camp, with-- fenced in like that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went there to have a look.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I saw, inside this place, people walking around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I saw this man, Weiss, coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's down there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I said-- And he came towards me, and standing on the other side of the fence, making this gesture, only to say, well, what can I do?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, you can do absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, we are lost.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We are doomed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was already aware of this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and then the following day, they were evacuated and-- and-- and sent to-- to-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another episode was when a Swedish lady married to a Hungarian Jew-- she was in Sweden.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got instructions from the Foreign Office to try to save her son, who was staying in the south of-- of Hungary, in-- in-- down at the Pecs.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is very far away.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
